name: Google Web Search - KDE SC 4.4, 2/2
description:
This user style transforms the Google Web Search (front page and search results) to match the default look of KDE SC 4.4 (Oxygen theme and colors).

ATTENTION: This style consists of two parts! In order to have it working correctly, you need to install both parts! Part 1 can be found here: http://userstyles.org/styles/27324

Changelog and more information can be found here: http://kde-look.org/content/show.php/?content=122968

discussions.name: Getting rid of the original google logo
